title: Gabooty's Tai Bwo Wannai Cooperative.

properties.name: description
properties.value: Gabooty's Tai Bwo Wannai Cooperative is a store located in Tai Bwo Wannai, owned by Gabooty. It sells machetes and villager clothing, and will buy semi-precious gems and gout tubers. Gabooty also runs Gabooty's Tai Bwo Wannai Drinky Store.

Gabooty's Tai Bwo Wannai Cooperative.
Released9 August 2005 (Update)
MembersYes
LocationTai Bwo Wannai
OwnerGabooty
SpecialtyMachetes, clothing
Location

Gabooty's Tai Bwo Wannai Cooperative is a store located in Tai Bwo Wannai, owned by Gabooty. It sells machetes and villager clothing, and will buy semi-precious gems and gout tubers. Gabooty also runs Gabooty's Tai Bwo Wannai Drinky Store.
